WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
This is Johnson's Zoo near Huntington in

2
00:00:02.800 --> 00:00:07.520
Cambridgeshire and as you can see there is a small police presence here this evening. Now the police

3
00:00:07.520 --> 00:00:14.480
we are told were called just before 1.30 this afternoon after a young child a three-year-old boy

4
00:00:14.480 --> 00:00:20.960
ended up in the crocodile enclosure. Now we understand he was then taken to Adam Brooks Hospital

5
00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:26.640
in Cambridgeshire which is around 15-20 miles away from here with serious injuries. We understand

6
00:00:26.640 --> 00:00:33.440
his condition is critical but stable and his family are being supported. Now the police have given an

7
00:00:33.440 --> 00:00:39.600
update they say they have arrested a 30-year-old man from Norfolk on suspicion of attempted murder

8
00:00:39.600 --> 00:00:45.200
and they believe that the boy and the man did not know each other. They are also investigating

9
00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:56.160
whether the boy's injuries were caused by any of the animals here.

